data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious "Prestige Series" of Hawk's Crest, nestled within the sought-after gated community of Winter Park. Immaculately maintained and boasting a builder's warranty, this 2021 gem exudes luxury and charm at every turn.  Step inside to discover a professionally designed interior adorned with exquisite custom woodwork gracing the family room and master bedroom. Marvel at the soaring cathedral ceilings and the elegance of wrought iron stairway spindles, perfectly complemented by the warmth of wood plank tile flooring.  The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, where culinary aspirations come to life amidst sleek quartz countertops, a farmhouse sink, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Entertain effortlessly with stacked ovens and a spacious island, while custom lighting sets the perfect ambiance for every occasion.  Experience true comfort and convenience with double-paned windows that invite natural light to dance throughout the home. With electronic remote blinds and role shades, you can effortlessly control the atmosphere to suit your mood.  Step outside to your private oasis, where a covered and extended patio beckons you to unwind in tranquility. Brick pavers lead the way to a serene view of the retention pond, offering ample backyard privacy for relaxation and entertainment.  Exemplifying elegance from every angle, this home features a tile roof and meticulous landscaping, all maintained by the HOA for your convenience. Experience the epitome of upscale living with access to Hawk's Crest amenities, including a guarded gate, community center, fitness center, pool, playground, and park.  With a brand new mirror, light fixtures, and stunning wallpaper, even the half bathroom exudes sophistication and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours and elevate your lifestyle to new heights. Schedule your showing today and prepare to be captivated by the allure of Hawk's Crest living. Measurements are appoximately.
